<p itemprop="description">一直想买一个物廉价美的安卓5G<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/zhinengshouji/" target="_blank">手机</a>做备用机，原来用的是<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/61727/" data-brandid="61727" target="_blank">红米</a>note3，双11玩喵币，输了好几场，虽然是怪我拉不到人，可是那速度，唉。在张大妈逡巡了很久，最终在11.11选择了<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/224981/" data-brandid="224981" target="_blank">realme</a> Q2 6+128，京东第三方发货，券后1149元，12号发货，13号收到。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">顺丰快递的盒子，</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx4dzz4/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202011/13/5faeabf8a01844664.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="刀已出鞘。"/></a>刀已出鞘。</span></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx4dzz4/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202011/13/5faeabf8d63f34850.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="打开一看，简约也简单，"/></a>打开一看，简约也简单，</span></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">拿出来看一看，</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx4dzz4/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202011/13/5faeabf91d8f62106.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="颜色和夕阳很配。"/></a>颜色和夕阳很配。</span></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">开盒子喽，</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx4dzz4/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202011/13/5faeacbd174b69537.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="安静的全家福。"/></a>安静的全家福。</span></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" style="line-height:0;">﻿</span></p><p itemprop="desc